column1: # This data comes from Table 3 in RFD 144.
# The "port #" refers to the port number on the VSC7448 switch.  The VLAN ID is
# calculated by adding 0x100 to that number.
# "Link Partner" identifies the entity which is connected to this port.
# The "vlan name" is the name assigned to the vlan link when it is created.
